OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of pupils missing lessons   
OL,6, because of Covid is stabilising in     
OL,7, England's state schools, despite a     
OL,8, record number of infections in the UK. 
OL,10,FNew government figures show 179,000    
OL,11,Fpupils (about 2.2%) were off last      
OL,12,FThursday because of the virus - down   
OL,13,Ffrom 202,000 (about 2.5%) in mid-March.
OL,15,FHowever, staffing problems remain in   
OL,16,Fsome schools, with almost one in 12    
OL,17,Fteachers absent.                       
OL,19,FAnd school leaders have criticised the 
OL,20,Fend of free testing in schools.        
